{"tid":473771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【登月真相？】太空人面罩見到呢個倒影 「證明登月係假嘅」","createTime":"2017-11-19T13:48:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-20T05:47:05.000Z","uid":47272,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a092384f34ae8910867fb0487cc15173048e8093","tid":473771,"uid":47272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T13:48:33.000Z","msg":"美國太空人到底是否真的有登陸月球，這個問題仍然爭論不休，有人堅稱是「大騙局」。<br />\n<br />\n有網民發現阿波羅17號（Apollo 17）登月任務的影片中出現「漏洞」，太空人面罩反映出另一個人，而這個人並沒穿上太空衣，認為是「登月造假」的有力證明。<br />\n阿波羅17號是美國太空總署第6次、亦是最後一次的登月任務，太空人塞爾南(Eugene Cernan)和施密特(Harrison Schmitt)在1972年12月成功登月，並花了22小時在月球進行一連串實驗。<br />\nYouTube用戶「Streetcap1」聲稱在阿波羅17號的登月照片上發現可疑畫面。「我覺得有點奇怪，所以我用軟件拍照。我發現一名沒有穿太空衣的人類」，他形容這個人「長頭髮、穿著類似背心」，他續說︰「到底我們是否真的有登月？他的太空衣呢？」<br />\n「Streetcap1」的發現再次引起新一輪的熱議，有人認為相片可信性不高，可能是「P圖」，也有人認為面罩倒影的人「是另一名拍照的太空人」，但亦有人相信這是有力證明：「這名『太空人』背上沒有維生儀器。」<br />\n英國《每日郵報》  <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/19/214722_2fc456d78016f50e6a6d191cd17722f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F19%2F214722_2fc456d78016f50e6a6d191cd17722f3.jpg&h=a6c41e7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171119/57476646\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171119%2F57476646&d=EqQJC1E0smmW6Oa1XPZok3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=3d3771e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171119%2F57476646&h=0c71d586\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171119/57476646</a>"},{"pid":"5315b276a70b4e84bb09f145408a536489d7cbcc","tid":473771,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T03:52:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bea6638c0d6242887407d42b3a06899643272f77","tid":473771,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T03:52:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f80ad7e0ac126a8e8d4784cedef5e731b2d1901","tid":473771,"uid":57023,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T03:56:45.000Z","msg":"圖片造假=/=登月做假"},{"pid":"6be3709cbda336d47a6b52d4dcc96230272b5ec1","tid":473771,"uid":40499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T04:02:54.000Z","msg":"真又好假又好 登月根本燒錢"},{"pid":"5b6add6a69cc80b56efbe5f70f60dd0ffdec6a16","tid":473771,"uid":35870,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T04:54:13.000Z","msg":"我諗起有張搞笑gif定一連串嘅圖<br />\n放大張圖係隻眼入面揾到第二塊鏡，跟住再放大，又揾到個車牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff243feab084fce902bce28f7977eedf68a40762","tid":473771,"uid":145365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T04:57:48.000Z","msg":"屌你老尾仲係度講假 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce1fa5c13e9dff16da74867db52a39f6e372147b","tid":473771,"uid":57023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T05:07:56.000Z","msg":"登月應係事實, 但公佈影片/圖片應不少是造假或經掩飾, 相信好多原片/圖唔敢公佈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"117027d634a5a1c3080833aac27114c499764e81","tid":473771,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T05:31:20.000Z","msg":"邊撚個話上太空一定要著太空衣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3979982ab7a714291eec7c714052857e47a3b760","tid":473771,"uid":14715,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T05:34:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我諗起有張搞笑gif定一連串嘅圖<br />\n放大張圖係隻眼入面揾到第二塊鏡，跟住再放大，又揾到個車牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/133400_840b927ea742f801c2e9e3c5110d6c4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F133400_840b927ea742f801c2e9e3c5110d6c4e.jpg&h=485fe546&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"46b3d9206eb9b498c0fc83b7fa8dc11f6369481a","tid":473771,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T05:35:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d3d157a5b1de9086e101a1b4d3ffac368e8f5191","tid":473771,"uid":10890,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T05:37:45.000Z","msg":"好早已經有人講過<br />\n登月係真<br />\n但當年冇人敢寫包單上到月球拍片一定傳到返地球<br />\n亦唔敢肯定可唔可以一路直播落去<br />\n所以事先拍定登陸月球嘅片<br />\n至要登陸到就可以播呢段片出街<br />\n<br />\n簡單講就係<br />\n段片係喺地球<br />\n但登陸月球係真"},{"pid":"8cf27aff1e34350e16285575c6af49a42f21cab8","tid":473771,"uid":60015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T05:42:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好早已經有人講過<br />\n登月係真<br />\n但當年冇人敢寫包單上到月球拍片一定傳到返地球<br />\n亦唔敢肯定可唔可以一路直播落去<br />\n所以事先拍定登陸月球嘅片<br />\n至要登陸到就可以播呢段片出街<br />\n<br />\n簡單講就係<br />\n段片係喺地球<br />\n但登陸月球係真</blockquote><br />\n咁點證明到登月係真？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d91f4448d925c5d71e65514afad29f4a9f42760","tid":473771,"uid":44646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T05:46:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好早已經有人講過<br />\n登月係真<br />\n但當年冇人敢寫包單上到月球拍片一定傳到返地球<br />\n亦唔敢肯定可唔可以一路直播落去<br />\n所以事先拍定登陸月球嘅片<br />\n至要登陸到就可以播呢段片出街<br />\n<br />\n簡單講就係<br />\n段片係喺地球<br />\n但登陸月球係真</blockquote><br />\n咁點證明到登月係真？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n假架，美國做假之後，蘇聯又唔踢爆佢，<br />\n之後中印日話用無人機登月都齊齊做假<br />\n原因係：<br />\n<br />\n根本無月球，呢個係有史以來所有當權者蒙蔽人民既陰謀"},{"pid":"2226b524b6614cef12ed597e7df469d770e75167","tid":473771,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T05:47:05.000Z","msg":"睇過billy bat就知登月一定係假"}]}